  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  clinical diagnosis of moderate to severe acne vulgaris

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  use of oral retinoid therapy in the past 12 months

          -  pregnancy, lactating, or planning to become pregnant

          -  excessive scarring in the treatment area, or other condition that would impact the
             ability to evaluate acne
      </textblock>
